STRICT CHAIN-OF-THOUGHT TASK — for EACH of your {{ num_inputs }} regexes,
the `reasoning` field MUST contain these FOUR labeled steps, IN ORDER,
before the final regex string is fixed:

  Step 1 (Quote): Copy ONE verbatim C++ branch condition from the RE2
