All four step labels — literally `Step 1 (Quote):`, `Step 2 (Locate):`,
`Step 3 (Construct):`, `Step 4 (Regex):` — MUST appear in the `reasoning`
string. Responses missing any label will be discarded.

Produce {{ num_inputs }} DISTINCT regex patterns. Keep each pattern
